<HEAD>CHAP. VII</HEAD>
<Q><L>&startq;Of aery tongues, that &s;yllable men's names</L>
<L>On &s;ands and &s;hores and de&s;ert wilderne&s;&s;es.&endq;</L>
<BIBL>MILTON.</BIBL></Q>
<P>It is now nece&s;&s;ary to mention &s;ome cir|cum&s;tance,
