the Signors heard the other night, all of a
&s;udden comes a great light, and, looking
behind me, there was a tall figure, (I &s;aw it
as plainly, ma'am&s;elle, as I &s;ee you at this
moment) a tall figure gliding along (Oh! I
cannot de&s;cribe how!) into the room that
